OL,6,FSix arrests have been made, and one
OL,7,Fperson has been charged, following
OL,8,Fviolent disorder outside a hotel
OL,9,Fhousing asylum seekers on Sunday.
OL,11,FAround 750 people were in attendance
OL,12,Fat the Holiday Inn Express in Wath-
OL,13,Fupon-Dearne, in Rotherham, when
OL,14,Fviolence broke out.
OL,16,FAssistant Chief Constable Lindsey
OL,17,FButterfield, of South Yorkshire
OL,18,FPolice, said: "So far we have had six
OL,19,Farrests, one in Sheffield and five in
OL,20,FRotherham, with one person already
OL,21,Fcharged before the court this morning.
