OL,6,F"Please be assured, we expect this
OL,7,Fnumber to increase significantly in
OL,8,Fthe coming days."
OL,10,FAt least 12 police officers were
OL,11,Finjured during the disorder, with
OL,12,Fitems such as bricks, fenceposts and
OL,13,Fbranches thrown at them.
OL,15,FACC Butterfield added: "Our police
OL,16,Fdogs suffered minor injuries after
OL,17,Fmissiles were launched at them and
OL,18,Fhorses had bricks, eggs, bottles and
OL,19,Fbeer cans thrown at their heads.
