OL,6,FMs Butterfield said an initial group
OL,7,Fof 250 people had arrived on Sunday
OL,8,Fmorning, with an additional 500
OL,9,Fjoining them shortly afterwards.
OL,11,FShe said the police believe they "held
OL,12,Ffar-right and anti-immigration views".
OL,14,F"At the same time, a large crowd began
OL,15,Fto gather in Sheffield city centre,
OL,16,Fdiverting a large number of force
OL,17,Fresources," Ms Butterfield added.
