OL,6,FSpeaking of the violence outside a
OL,7,Fhotel in Rotherham, she said: "There
OL,8,Fwas a particularly sickening moment
OL,9,Fwhen a wheelie bin was pushed against
OL,10,Fthe hotel and set on fire with the
OL,11,Fclear intent to cause serious harm to
OL,12,Fthe residents and staff.
OL,14,F"It was known there were people
OL,15,Fresiding and working in the hotel but
OL,16,Fthe mindless individuals responsible
OL,17,Fhad absolutely no regard for their
OL,18,Fsafety.
